WEBVTT

00:07:29.083 --> 00:07:31.515
our friends assumed I would do
what everyone does,

00:07:31.539 --> 00:07:33.674
which is say goodbye
and send her to Earth,

00:07:34.517 --> 00:07:37.732
so that none of us
would have to look at her

00:07:37.756 --> 00:07:41.492
or be around her
or think about her and her ...

00:07:42.225 --> 00:07:43.858
failure to keep living.

00:07:48.811 --> 00:07:49.995
More than anything,

00:07:50.019 --> 00:07:52.796
they didn't want to be around
her actual physical body.

00:07:52.820 --> 00:07:55.824
They kept referring to it as "declining,"

00:07:56.536 --> 00:07:58.801
even though she herself
was fascinated by it,

00:07:58.825 --> 00:08:00.948
the changes it was going through,